---
---

<section style={{display: "grid", gridTemplateColumns: "1.45fr .55fr", borderBottom: "2px solid var(--color-border-strong)", minHeight: "660px"}}>
  <div style={{padding: "64px 36px 44px", display: "flex", flexDirection: "column", justifyContent: "space-between", borderRight: "2px solid var(--color-border-strong)"}}>
    <div>
      <div style={{marginBottom: "28px"}}>
        <span style={{display: "inline-block", background: "var(--color-accent)", padding: "5px 8px", font: "700 13px/1.4 ui-monospace,monospace", textTransform: "uppercase", letterSpacing: ".04em", color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>Product &times; Business &times; AI</span>
      </div>
      <h1 style={{fontSize: "clamp(60px,9vw,120px)", lineHeight: ".88", letterSpacing: "-.075em", margin: "0 0 36px", fontWeight: 900, maxWidth: "1050px"}}>
        拆掉假设，<br />重构业务。
      </h1>
      <p style={{fontSize: "clamp(18px,2vw,28px)", lineHeight: 1.4, maxWidth: "820px", margin: 0, color: "var(--color-text-primary)"}}>
        从第一性原理出发，识别业务真正的问题，用 AI 原生方式重新设计产品与增长系统。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div style={{font: "700 13px/1.5 ui-monospace,monospace", color: "var(--color-text-muted)"}}>
      KAKARROT / 产品经理与 AI 实践者<br />
      写作 &middot; 案例 &middot; 独立研究
    </div>
  </div>
  <aside style={{display: "flex", flexDirection: "column"}}>
    <div style={{padding: "28px", font: "700 13px/1 ui-monospace,monospace", borderBottom: "2px solid var(--color-border-strong)"}}>INDEX / 001</div>
    <div style={{flex: 1, background: "var(--color-text-primary)", color: "var(--color-bg-warm)", display: "flex", alignItems: "center", justifyContent: "center", textAlign: "center", padding: "30px"}}>
      <div>
        <strong style={{fontSize: "clamp(64px,7vw,88px)", letterSpacing: "-.08em", fontWeight: 900}}>K</strong>
        <small style={{display: "block", font: "700 14px/1.7 ui-monospace,monospace", letterSpacing: ".08em", marginTop: "14px"}}>THINK FROM ZERO<br />BUILD FOR REALITY</small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>
</section>
